column1: # Title: Building default technology efficiency for gcameurope
# Source: Same as gcamusa A44.globaltech_eff. Heat pumps have been removed and traditional biomass and district heat have been added
column2: as well as some biomass and coal technologies for different supplysectors. Unpublished inputs to the NEMS model; provided by EIA. Assumptions are simliar to the 2016 Annual Energy Outlook (Table 22; https://www.eia.gov/outlooks/aeo/data/browser/#/?id=30-AEO2016&cases=ref2016~ref_no_cpp&sourcekey=0).
